Hello Everyone,

Looks like M15 internal structure shift to bullish , so we will count as counter trend.
H4,D1 structure is still bearish, so we have to wait for price to come at H4/M15 zone.

So buy/sell with confirmation and take risk max 1%.

Good luck

What this chart pattern shows us is a loss of trend strength and a deceleration in price movement.

The most achievable projection for setting our take profit will be the maximum width of the pattern, which occurs at the beginning of it. Alternatively, you can take the level that marks the start of the correction as a profit-taking point.
